                  <div class="Container-H2">
                   <!--Container Title-->
                   <div class="dnntitle">
                    <h2>
                     <span class="title-H2" id="dnn_ctr3880_dnnTITLE_titleLabel">
                      Canandaigua Medical Group
                     </span>
                    </h2>
                   </div>
                   <!--Container Title End-->
                   <!--Container Content-->
                   <div class="contentmain">
                    <div class="contentpane" id="dnn_ctr3880_ContentPane">
                     <!-- Start_Module_3880 -->
                     <div class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC" id="dnn_ctr3880_ModuleContent">
                      <div class="Normal" id="dnn_ctr3880_HtmlModule_lblContent">
                       <span style="background-color: rgb(31, 73, 125); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                        Part of F.F. Thompson Hospital
                       </span>
                       <p>
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        <b style="">
                         <span style="font-size: 18px;">
                          Welcome to the Thompson Health Canandaigua Medical Group practice!
                         </span>
                         <br/>
                        </b>
                        <b>
                         OB/GYN  Pediatrics  Adult Medicine  Surgery
                        </b>
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        Thompson Health acquired Canandaigua Medical Group on May 7, 2018. With this acquisition comes a
                        <a href="/About-Us/Thompson-Health-Canandaigua-Medical-Group">
                         new building
                        </a>
                        slated to open in early 2019, the benefit of more accepted insurances (matching those accepted by F.F. Thompson Hospital), an updated electronic medical record system to be introduced in July 2018.
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        This multi-specialty medical practice is committed toproviding the highest quality, comprehensive health care to its patients. Your physician team provides the care you need today and supports you in making choices that will keep you healthy in the years to come.
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        The Canandaigua Medical Group has two facilities. The main facility is located in Canandaigua, directly across the street from F.F. Thompson Hospital. The other facility -which contains satellite pediatric and OB/GYN offices - is located in the Thompson Medical Center in Farmington.
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        <strong>
                         Canandaigua Office:
                        </strong>
                        <br/>
                        335 Parrish Street
                        <br/>
                        Canandaigua, New York, 14424
                        <br/>
                        (585) 393-2888
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        Office Hours:
                        <br/>
                        Monday-Friday: 8 a.m. 5 p.m.
                        <br/>
                        Saturday: 8 a.m. 12 noon (Pediatrics only)
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        Thompson Health
                        <a href="/Health-Services/Laboratory-Medicine">
                         Lab Draw Station
                        </a>
                        services available at the Canandaigua location.
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        <strong>
                         Farmington Office (Pediatrics and OB/GYN only):
                        </strong>
                        <br/>
                        1160 Corporate Drive
                        <br/>
                        Farmington, New York 14425
                        <br/>
                        (585) 924-2030 (Pediatrics)
                        <br/>
                        (585) 924-8686 (Obstetrics/Gynecology)
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        Office Hours:
                        <br/>
                        Monday-Friday: 8 a.m. 5 p.m.
                       </p>
                       <p>
                        Thompson Health
                        <a href="/Health-Services/Laboratory-Medicine">
                         Lab Draw Station
                        </a>
                        and
                        <a href="/Health-Services/Diagnostic-Imaging/X-ray">
                         X-ray
                        </a>
                        , plus UR Medicine
                        <a href="/Health-Services/Emergency-Medicine/Urgent-Care">
                         Urgent Care
                        </a>
                        Services are available at theFarmington location.
                       </p>
